name: Lieutenant Page
Lore: 'Scout who served under General Veers'' command. Defected and was recruited by General Madine''s commando organization. Works closely with Colonel Cracken.',
Text: 'Adds 1 to each of your battle destiny draws when with Derlin, Cracken or Madine at a site (or when with at least two of your other scouts at an exterior planet site). Your Rebel scouts deploy -1 to same exterior site (except Rebel Landing Site).',
